1.0.2.name: wordpress/spotgrab
1.0.2.description:
SpotGrab features videos of rental properties in your area with great maps to help you grab your new place. Find your spot. Grab it.

The Plugin was developed at Startup Weekend Boulder 2009.

  • Thanks Andrew Hyde for putting together this AWESOME event!

The SpotGrab Plugin:

  • Displays SpotGrab properties in the blog sidebar.
  • Please see the Screenshots for examples.

SpotGrab Team Members:

  • Matt Bernier - Team leader
  • Michael Euperio
  • Tim Falls
  • Grant Grigor
